{
  "stem": "25209.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It'll all go away if you don't take any notice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And nobody else was panicking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you know, we'll be all right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But-- but there was-- there was a lot to of unrest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was a lot of, you know, fear about what's happening.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, they were constantly listening to the news.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as a kid, you didn't sort of think about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You didn't-- [LAUGHS] I remember saying to my mother when we were running, are we chasing the Germans or are the Germans chasing us?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, you sort of lost track because you never knew where the front was and who was running where.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a confusing I think is probably the best way to describe it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was extremely confusing, because it didn't make sense.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, you get smacked if you're naughty.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You get punished if your bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What was happening?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Didn't have a clue.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it made for a lot of anxiety.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Did your parents plan to leave in case something happened?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my father wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father had this real sixth sense about self preservation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother didn't want to go because none of her friends were going.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he said, we're going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he usually wasn't very bossy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But this time he said, we're going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so he said, look, we're just pretend we're going on a holiday, and we'll pack the car.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we'll just drive deeper into Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We're not crossing any borders.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he prepared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was just a little bit before the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, you will ask me how little.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would say, looking at it now, a couple of months, say three month, four month-- wouldn't be anymore than that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Orlova was Polish.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
